de_saunahouse
=============

De_saunahouse is a map ported from CS:GO to CS:S.
CS:GO version: http://csgo.gamebanana.com/maps/168067

Doesn't look as good as in CS:GO though - Originally ported for my temp server

Map contains:

- 3 routes to use

- 2 pools

- 1 sauna

- 1 toilet

- 2 dressing rooms

- 1 cafeternia

- 1 office area

- 1 fighting hallway


- 1 lobby

- Outside area
